## Airtable API Bridge
A set of webhooks for easier access to Airtable bases data via Airtable API from outside Airtable as well as from Airtable apps. Overcomes the built-in Airtable sync timing issue, works immediately while Airtable built-in sync runs only once every 5 minutes. Controls the Airtable API rate limits, creating queue in case of request exceeds the allowed rate.

Can connect to multiple tables from multiple Airtable bases via [[Public Website/Monito.website Data Hub|Monito.website Data Hub]]

### 1. get at data

***Endpoint:***

```bash
Method: POST
Type: JSON
URL: http://localhost/getDataFromAt
```


***Headers:***

| Key | Value | Description |
| --- | ------|-------------|
| x-api-key | 12345678 |  |



***Body:***

```js        
{
    "requestId": "7f70e1cf-96c7-4565-91ad-e5d815956af8"
}
```

***Responce:***

```js
{
    "readData": [
        {
            "recordId": "rec8U7oAXlusK1PPr",
            "fields": {
                "Name": "A167",
                "cpu": 0
            },
            "baseId": "app6CBBHqZGdxF5ba",
            "tableName": "vps"
        },
        {
            "recordId": "recKcw978ThQuvgT5",
            "fields": {
                "Name": "A219",
                "cpu": 0
            },
            "baseId": "app6CBBHqZGdxF5ba",
            "tableName": "vps"
        },
        {
            "recordId": "recgpnkODQmgKfNct",
            "fields": {
                "Name": "default",
                "cpu": 0.08
            },
            "baseId": "app6CBBHqZGdxF5ba",
            "tableName": "vps"
        }
    ],
    "writeData": [
        {
            "recordId": "recdwEv8XRiWgeTgc",
            "fields": {
                "memory": 1,

        }

}
```



### 2. send data to at



***Endpoint:***

```bash
Method: POST
Type: JSON
URL: http://localhost/sendDataToAt
```


***Headers:***

| Key | Value | Description |
| --- | ------|-------------|
| x-api-key | 12345678 |  |



***Body:***

```js        
{
    "data": {
        "read": [
            {
                "baseId": "app6CBBHqZGdxF5ba",
                "tableName": "vps",
                "fields": ["Name", "cpu"],
                // https://support.airtable.com/hc/en-us/articles/203255215-Formula-Field-Reference#logical
                "filterByFormula": "OR(id='recgpnkODQmgKfNct',OS='2019')"
            }
        ],
        "write": [{
            "baseId": "app6CBBHqZGdxF5ba",
            "tableName": "vps",
            "records": [
                // update existed record
                {
                    "recordId": "recDaknz6a4lt1oHi", 
                    "fields": { 
                            "cpu": 0.5,
                            "memory": 0.5
                        }
                },
                // create new record
                {
                    "fields": { 
                            "cpu": 1,
                            "memory": 1
                        }
                }
            ]
        }]
    }   
}
```

***Responce:***

```js
{
    "requestId": "7f70e1cf-96c7-4565-91ad-e5d815956af8",
    "status": "wait"
}
```
